{"tid":1242890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小心政府軟皮蛇","createTime":"2019-06-19T08:41:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T00:10:59.000Z","uid":78184,"like":52,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f513461a239e1198ad1d9b877040ba167d600b27","tid":1242890,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:41:56.000Z","msg":"政府今日將有爭議的項目全部唔傾住，明日大嶼、國歌法都唔繼續住，擺明以退為進。<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好俾政府帶住走。因為如果政府突然放軟哂，好唔正常！我覺得政府間接就係想大家21/6搞大佢，證明我們是暴徒搞亂社會，然後讓林鄭搶返個民意道德高地，咁之後佢同班保皇黨就會翻生，再挾返民意黎處理爭議性項目。<br />\n<br />\n所以而家政府一下子放軟哂，我地到時21/6太激進就會可能累事，千祈唔好俾機會政府逆轉！"},{"pid":"578cef794332f555dc3bce156df621af82cd00e2","tid":1242890,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:58:56.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"2aa03563ee07b44e342f7c9b6a27e0f88cea2ee1","tid":1242890,"uid":2617,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:59:48.000Z","msg":"去齋坐囉"},{"pid":"572a51eaccaf9306de278c706201715eab26ec7e","tid":1242890,"uid":262690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:00:16.000Z","msg":"CLS, 佢放軟我地佔撚晒佢叫柒婆出嚟對話!!!"},{"pid":"f0ee31f9a451a4735c065519e089f5ae278a8091","tid":1242890,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:00:47.000Z","msg":"我地不嬲唔會主動衝擊<br />\n防守為主"},{"pid":"13f7237250c5ec95c93762b8c0ac19df66190b39","tid":1242890,"uid":22288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:01:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"81bf1ea53b59e87974f32c37220c02ef4965ad27","tid":1242890,"uid":114186,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:01:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">到時唔好作出咁激烈行為 提防港共有位入比班狗升級武力!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"72bb583b4d6d4403dd5c060a61e9fc38b659fbf0","tid":1242890,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:02:00.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"13ad5523717467412f88ade243851abbdde58aac","ti